Description: Yandex smart home with Alice to MQTT for Wiren Board controllers
 A bridge between Yandex Alice voice assistant and Wiren Board MQTT-based
 smart home system. This package allows users to control devices connected
 to Wiren Board controllers using voice commands through Yandex Alice smart
 speakers and other compatible devices.
